discount to spot prices. Funding payments occur at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC between long and short position holders. The zero maker fee structure significantly reduces entry/exit costs for arbitrage strategies, though taker fees of 0.03% still apply for market orders."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
